citeinfo.title: Administrative Boundaries (Parish) Census of Housing, Immigration, and Living Conditions Ecuador 2010

descript.abstract: This polygon dataset represents the 2010 population census performed in Ecuador at the level three administrative level (known as parishes or parroquias), with census data for housing, immigration, and living conditions.
descript.purpose: This dataset is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
